<title>UK: Bridon says performing better than in 1996.</title>
<headline>Bridon says performing better than in 1996.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-05-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>Bridon Plc, a wire, rope and industrial textiles group, said on Thursday that it has continued to perform at better levels than in 1996.  </p>
<p>The company told shareholders at its annual meeting that it has seen improved order books in its manufactured products businesses.</p>
<p>Bridon said that results at its unit Certex have been lower than in 1996, but it expects to see an improvement in coming months despite flat markets in Continental Europe.</p>
